# ============================================================
# HFWastelandZ — Admins / Player Roles
# Copy this file to:  $profile:HFWastelandZ_admins.conf
# ============================================================
#
# This file decides each player's ROLE (their permission tier),
# keyed by Steam64 ID. The server is the only machine that reads
# it — players cannot fake their role.
#
# THE FIVE ROLES  (higher number = more power)
#   OWNER    40   you — full control, including server restart
#   ADMIN    30   full admin: Game Master (Zeus), promote others, save, etc.
#   MOD      20   moderator: kick, ban, mute, teleport, heal, god, announce
#   TRUSTED  10   donor / verified helper (reserved for future perks)
#   EVERYONE  0   default — every normal player (no line needed)
#
# FORMAT  (one player per line)
#   <ROLE> <Steam64ID>
#
# Steam64 IDs are 17-digit numbers. Find one at https://steamid.io
# or from a Steam profile URL. Anyone NOT listed here is EVERYONE.
#
# EXAMPLE
#   OWNER   76561198000000001
#   ADMIN   76561198000000002
#   MOD     76561198000000003
#   TRUSTED 76561198000000004
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# HOW TO SET SOMEONE'S ROLE
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 1) FIRST admin (and the ONLY way to set OWNER): edit this file.
#    Add a line like  OWNER 7656119...  then restart the server.
#
# 2) After that, do it live in-game (no restart) with the command:
#       /admin promote <name|playerId> <EVERYONE|TRUSTED|MOD|ADMIN>
#    - You must be ADMIN or OWNER to use it.
#    - It can NEVER grant OWNER (that stays file-only, on purpose,
#      so nobody can lock you out). OWNER is set by editing here.
#    - It rewrites this file for you, so the change survives restarts.
#
# SEE WHO HAS WHAT ROLE
#       /admin who        (lists everyone online with their role)
#
# WHAT EACH ROLE CAN DO
#   Each command has a minimum role. Defaults, for example:
#     MOD    — /admin who, kick, ban, mute, tp, heal, god, announce
#     ADMIN  — /admin promote, save, debug; all /mission and /spot editing
#     OWNER  — /admin restart
#   You can change any command's required role in
#   HFWastelandZ_command_tiers.conf (see that file).
#
# BEHAVIOR
#   No file / empty file  → no admins; Game Master access denied for all.
# ============================================================

# --- ROLES ---  (uncomment and use your own Steam64 IDs)
# OWNER 76561198000000001
# ADMIN 76561198000000002
# MOD   76561198000000003
